    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩Demo现已开放，欢迎大家体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家交流QQ群：1020782877</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏还在开发的前期阶段，仍有许多设计的不完善之处和程序bug，欢迎大家在讨论区反馈，我们会持续对此试玩版进行更新，并努力完善正式版的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谢谢大家~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《摸鱼仙村》，一款结合放置与建造的修仙游戏。在这里，你将化身仙境造物主，搭建村落、调配资源、培育修士，让一方洞天焕发生机，开启属于你的逍遥修仙之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>卡牌建造，规划仙村</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集卡牌搭建建筑，打造独一无二的仙村格局。伐木采矿、村民调配，每一步布局都决定你的修真格局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/23ab44633bd94d92620bffecb6a32afb.poster.avif?t=1749708922\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/23ab44633bd94d92620bffecb6a32afb.webm?t=1749708922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>集结队伍，掠夺资源</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在确定自己仙村的宗门后，可以根据独特的战斗风格整合一批强力的斗士，再从Steam排行榜上挑选其他玩家的仙村，入侵掠夺更强力的修炼资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/66c9b0941172f28e6c7107cde319c92e.poster.avif?t=1749708922\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/66c9b0941172f28e6c7107cde319c92e.webm?t=1749708922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>摸鱼修真，效率至上</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最小化浮窗后台运行，暗中摸鱼也能修仙不断。上班建村两不误，效率与逍遥同行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/65f3444bea2d4e992548688eb58be50f.poster.avif?t=1749708922\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/65f3444bea2d4e992548688eb58be50f.webm?t=1749708922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索秘境，战斗突破</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掷骰前行，步步皆奇遇。突发事件、强敌挑战、小游戏试炼，资源与机缘并存，每一步都是新篇章。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/ca25882a8e20dd19ded9ad79e3125c19.poster.avif?t=1749708922\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/ca25882a8e20dd19ded9ad79e3125c19.webm?t=1749708922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多元系统，丰富玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >炼丹制器、宗门修炼、天赋突破，多元系统互相联动。从生产经营到战斗升级，修仙之路充满可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/c2ef34c6b5dd62be2a4a90f18bfed799.poster.avif?t=1749708922\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/c2ef34c6b5dd62be2a4a90f18bfed799.webm?t=1749708922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>轻松挂机，资源自来</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需繁复操作，资源自动采集，离线也能持续进账。轻松放置、轻点升级，修炼之路从不设限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/846a5c114de6ac69a096474d63be2832.poster.avif?t=1749708922\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/846a5c114de6ac69a096474d63be2832.webm?t=1749708922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >修仙之路，从摸鱼开始。放置养成，自由建造，随时随地畅享一段自在逍遥的仙村人生！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/3bd8916c59b4771c58b510d3a2ddc291.webp?t=1749708922\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224850/extras/3bd8916c59b4771c58b510d3a2ddc291.poster.avif?t=1749708922\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=100 /></picture></span></p>",
